name: Last swaps in H=N (v2)
description: This tool displays the last swaps in H=N for a given price range. Note that the swap might have been cancelled after that or the editions could have been collected already. This tool is powered by the TzKT API and might not work in the future if the API calls change. In fact, this is an update of OBJKT#126431 which stopped to work because the H=N marketplace contract address changed. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
